1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
ظآزHush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pondظآز

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
ظآزA shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chestظآز

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزI would shield youظآز

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
ظآزFrom this cruel wind and frostظآز

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
ظآزThe russet cloth
brushes against my heartظآز

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
ظآزLike sunset
draping over your shouldersظآز

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
ظآزThis lingering afterglowظآز

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
ظآزHolds the image
of our very first glanceظآز

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
ظآزI borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze windowظآز

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
ظآزTailoring moonlight
into your luminous gownظآز

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
ظآزSevering the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendorظآز

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
ظآزWith a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hairظآز

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
ظآزPouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wearظآز

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
ظآزIn this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradiseظآز

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 3=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,280
My lord,

18
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:22,360
it's time to let the wind
from the capital blow in.

19
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,520
Good.

20
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,840
By my order,

21
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,520
spread the word across the city:

22
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:33,920
the Zhou family's Rustling Silk

23
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:36,680
has been stripped
of its imperial tribute status.

24
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,880
Understood.

25
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,240
Yu,

26
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:54,840
this is

27
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:57,240
the Rustling Silk
for the imperial tribute?

28
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,440
Yes, no doubt about it.

29
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,160
I made every piece of this myself.

30
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:06,840
Alright, you can go now.

31
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,920
Do you trust me?

32
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,240
Yeah, I do.

33
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,280
Listen to me.

34
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:13,040
Pack your things right now.

35
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,480
Leave the Zhou family with me.

36
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,880
We'll go as far as we can.

37
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,080
Why?

38
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:19,560
The Zhous are about
to face utter disaster.

39
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,440
Wait.

40
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,240
Li Yunhe,

41
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:21,840
what are you talking about?

42
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,680
I don't understand.

43
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,640
The Zhou family is doing fine.

44
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,040
How could a disaster be coming?

45
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:25,880
Do you remember

46
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,640
what I said at Zhou's Fabrics?

47
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,720
The Rustling Silk on the market

48
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,920
is only average quality.

49
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:33,200
But the silk
made for the imperial tribute

50
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,160
is all top-tier.

51
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,840
About what you just showed me,

52
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,840
even putting quality aside,

53
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,600
the most basic quality control

54
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:40,840
is wildly inconsistent.

55
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:43,120
The imperial court isn't stupid.

56
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,120
If they find quality issues,

57
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:46,480
at the very least,

58
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:48,640
they'll strip
the Zhous' imperial tribute status.

59
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:49,880
At worst,

60
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:52,080
they'll charge us
with deceiving the throne,

61
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,720
which means
execution of the entire clan.

62
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,520
Is our Rustling Silk

63
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,440
really that inferior?

64
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:03,080
That's not something a hired hand
should worry about.

65
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,520
This isn't your problem.

66
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,960
How is this not my problem?

67
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,120
I'm the Zhou...

68
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,680
Yu!

69
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,320
Yu, bad news!

70
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,560
The whole city is buzzing with talk.

71
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,960
The Zhou family's Rustling Silk

72
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,640
is losing its imperial tribute status!

73
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,680
What?

74
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:18,200
It's already spreading?

75
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:25,560
(Xianquan Tavern)

76
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,840
(Xianquan Tavern)
The Zhou household pre-sold

77
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,720
a huge quantity
of tribute-grade Rustling Silk.

78
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:31,120
But when buyers realize
they've been duped,

79
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,720
they'll storm the place
demanding answers.

80
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,000
In other words,

81
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,240
the Zhous

82
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,800
have been completely screwed over
by Li Yunhe.

83
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:43,040
I'd like to see how he plans
to dig himself out of this hole.

84
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,120
Wait, something's off.

85
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,480
The news about Rustling Silk

86
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,080
losing its tribute status

87
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,760
couldn't have reached Feng City
this fast.

88
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,520
News from the capital
doesn't travel that quickly.

89
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:54,720
Unless someone deliberately leaked it.

90
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,520
Ah, I see.

91
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:01,920
You're getting more and more devious,
Yunzhuo.

92
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:04,800
You think I'd do something like that?

93
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:07,000
The one who leaked this news

94
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:09,160
was at the Marquis House.

95
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,920
The Marquis House?

96
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,400
The Marquis's heir

97
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,960
has his eye on the Zhou heiress.

98
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,600
But Ms. Zhou, unexpectedly,

99
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,720
got that nobody, Li Yunhe,
to be her husband.

100
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,600
So there's bad blood between them.

101
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,000
A few days ago,

102
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:25,360
the woman who caused a scene
at Zhou's Fabrics

103
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,360
was sent by Lu Qifeng.

104
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,640
God bless you.

105
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,520
Oh, my lord,

106
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,920
have you caught a chill?

107
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:36,520
Someone must be badmouthing me.

108
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,120
Yunzhuo,

109
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,320
how about you do me a favor later?

110
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:43,240
Save Li Yunhe from the Marquis House.

111
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,000
Then,

112
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,040
castrate him and send him to the palace.

113
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,080
Let him have a taste

114
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:50,720
of being scammed for once.

115
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,440
Ridiculous!

116
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:58,820
(Zhou Manor)

117
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,320
Ugh, stop pacing already.

118
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,920
You're making my head spin.

119
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,120
It's not like I want to pace.

120
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,520
What did I tell you back then?

121
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,520
I said Li Yunhe was of poor character,

122
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,320
but you wouldn't listen.

123
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,560
Look what's happening.

124
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,560
You should've just divorced him
right away.

125
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,600
Rustling Silk losing its tribute status

126
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,840
was decided by His Majesty.

127
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,360
It has nothing to do with Mr. Li.

128
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,320
You're always about Mr. Li.

129
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,520
Never stopped talking about him.

130
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,320
Why don't you just go
share a room with him?

131
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,240
Hey!

132
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:34,920
Enough.

133
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:37,880
Huaijin,

134
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:39,480
do you have

135
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,720
inside information or something?

136
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,840
Do you know where the news

137
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,760
about Rustling Silk
losing its tribute status

138
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,520
comes from?

139
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,720
Could it be...

140
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,120
I don't know.

141
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,600
It came from the Marquis House.

142
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,840
The one that good-for-nothing offended

143
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,360
is the Marquis's heir.

144
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,240
Yu,

145
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:05,800
do I need to spell it out any clearer?

146
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,360
Alright.

147
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,760
I get it.

148
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,880
I'll verify

149
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,200
whether this news is true.

150
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:14,960
Also,

151
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:17,840
though Li Yunhe
signed the divorce letter,

152
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:19,120
I haven't,

153
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,840
so he's still my husband.

154
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,640
You need to watch your words
from now on, Huaijin.

155
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:24,720
What...

156
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,840
Why can't I get through to you?

157
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,600
My lady, maybe...

158
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,200
Maybe you should just come clean
with Mr. Li.

159
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,080
He might have a way
to save the Zhou family.

160
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:42,920
Yu.

161
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,720
What brings you here?

162
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,480
Why do you look so pale?

163
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:51,080
Did Ms. Zhou bully you?

164
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,040
Come on,

165
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,200
I'll go confront her with you.

166
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,200
No.

167
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,480
I'm fine.

168
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,520
She really didn't give you a hard time?

169
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:13,120
I ran into her on my way here earlier.

170
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,840
She looked absolutely furious.

171
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,920
And now you're so pale.

172
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,200
Honestly, the Zhou household
treats me pretty well.

173
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,120
Maybe you should just leave.

174
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,480
You already signed
the divorce letter anyway.

175
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,440
Whatever happens to the Zhous
now has nothing to do with you.

176
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,680
Yu,

177
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:30,920
has work fried your brain?

178
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,800
What good is their kindness?

179
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,000
When they need you,

180
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,280
you're their best friend in the world.

181
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,240
When they don't,

182
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,480
you're still just a servant.

183
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,200
Like what happened just now.

184
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,920
Can you look me in the eye and tell me

185
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,120
she didn't give you a hard time?

186
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,240
Chunxiang,

187
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,200
come here.

188
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,240
What did Ms. Zhou

189
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,960
say to Yu just now?

190
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,480
Ms. Zhou?

191
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:57,920
Ms. Zhou...

192
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:04,080
She came to tell Yu

193
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:07,000
about us losing

194
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,440
the imperial tribute status.

195
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,040
That's right.

196
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,520
We were just discussing

197
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:14,360
Rustling Silk

198
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:16,640
losing its tribute status.

199
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,320
She really didn't give you trouble?

200
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,240
No.

201
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:24,320
Ask Chunxiang if you don't believe me.

202
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:25,880
Ms. Zhou came to ask Yu

203
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,160
if she had any solution.

204
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,960
Solution, my foot.

205
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:30,280
The Zhou family

206
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:32,520
clearly has flaws
in their Rustling Silk craft.

207
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,560
Instead of fixing their process

208
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:35,520
and quality control,

209
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:37,200
they come to hassle a hired hand?

210
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,240
They deserve

211
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,960
to lose their tribute status.

212
00:08:42,560 --> 00:08:43,280
Mr. Li,

213
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,200
Ms. Zhou

214
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,760
really didn't bully Yu.

215
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:47,920
She said the craft manual

216
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:50,080
for making Rustling Silk

217
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,040
was destroyed

218
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:52,760
ten years ago in a fire.

219
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,320
So she came to ask Yu

220
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,880
if there was any way to fix this.

221
00:08:58,520 --> 00:08:59,960
That troubled look
on your face earlier...

222
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,160
Were you thinking about how to restore

223
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,640
the core craft of Rustling Silk?

224
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:05,240
When the city gate catches fire,

225
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,360
the fish in the moat suffer.

226
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,880
Today, I want to tell you

227
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:11,120
that when the nest falls,
no egg remains whole.

228
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,440
In your eyes,

229
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,920
I'm just a servant of the Zhou family.

230
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,280
But in my opinion,

231
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,160
I grew up with the Zhous.

232
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,160
My feelings toward them...

233
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,240
Oh, forget it.

234
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,080
Since you want to stay,

235
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,560
I'll stay too.

236
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:26,040
I'll help the Zhous one last time.

237
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,200
Li Yunhe,

238
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,360
are you truly willing

239
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,720
to stay and help me?

240
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:36,640
"Willing" might be pushing it.

241
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:39,520
After all, you made your choice.

242
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,400
I'm impressed.

243
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:41,520
Great!

244
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:45,400
Come on,

245
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,120
Chunxiang, let's get to work.

246
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:47,640
Alright.

247
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:55,920
Well, this is a pleasant surprise.

248
00:10:04,580 --> 00:10:06,340
ظآزI awake a thousand years laterظآز

249
00:10:06,340 --> 00:10:09,300
ظآزIn this unfamiliar placeظآز

250
00:10:11,940 --> 00:10:13,780
ظآزYou wait a thousand miles awayظآز

251
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:17,020
ظآزIn those mottled, fading daysظآز

252
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:19,420
(Zhou Manor)

253
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:22,380
ظآزSee the silk blanket the long hallwayظآز

254
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:26,060
ظآزSteamings, boiling,
time turns yellowed and wornظآز

255
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:28,780
ظآزI shift the warp and weftظآز

256
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:32,220
ظآزCalculating the sharp edges of fateظآز

257
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:37,260
ظآزThe russet cloth
brushes against my heartظآز

258
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:41,060
ظآزLike sunset
draping over your shouldersظآز

259
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:43,380
ظآزThis lingering afterglowظآز

260
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:47,220
ظآزHolds the image
of our very first glanceظآز

261
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:51,900
ظآزI borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze windowظآز

262
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:56,220
ظآزTailoring moonlight
into your luminous gownظآز

263
00:10:56,700 --> 00:11:02,620
ظآزSevering the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendorظآز

264
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:06,780
ظآزWith a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hairظآز

265
00:11:07,020 --> 00:11:10,500
ظآزPouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wearظآز

266
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:17,460
ظآزIn this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradiseظآز

267
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,040
It really is different.

268
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:39,440
Exactly.

269
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,240
The quality of this batch
of Rustling Silk

270
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:43,040
is absolutely on par
with the tribute-grade piece,

271
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,640
maybe even better.

272
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:45,760
The key is

273
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:47,280
that these dozen or so bolts

274
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,640
are completely consistent in quality.

275
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:50,040
That's great, Yu.

276
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:52,040
With the Rustling Silk's quality
improved,

277
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:54,120
the Zhou family
won't go bankrupt after all.

278
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:54,960
Indeed.

279
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:56,400
Li Yunhe,

280
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:58,360
we owe you big this time.

281
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,840
Mr. Li, why don't you look

282
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,160
the least bit excited?

283
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,440
What's there to be excited about?

284
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:08,880
Through scientific testing,

285
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,120
the quality of Rustling Silk

286
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,600
has been improved,

287
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,760
exactly as expected.

288
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:15,000
Besides,

289
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:17,840
restoring the Zhous'
core Rustling Silk craft?

290
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,680
What's that got to do
with a cast-off son-in-law

291
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,600
like me?

292
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:22,600
Don't say that, Li Yunhe.

293
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,240
The recovery
of Rustling Silk's core craft

294
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,200
wouldn't have happened

295
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,320
without your contribution.

296
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:28,360
The Zhou family
will definitely remember this kindness.

297
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,000
Oh, no, no.

298
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,840
I don't need them
to remember my kindness.

299
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:35,200
I just hope they'll remember
the good deeds you've done

300
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,560
and won't give you a hard time

301
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,120
when the time comes to buy your freedom.

302
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,240
Speaking of which,

303
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:43,400
the name "Rustling Silk"?

304
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,800
Maybe it's time to drop it.

305
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:48,080
You mean renaming it?

306
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,520
But why?

307
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,440
Because

308
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:53,080
Rustling Silk has been stripped

309
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,720
of its imperial tribute status.

310
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:57,120
If we keep using that name,

311
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:59,520
it might leave a bad impression
on everyone.

312
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:00,960
That's the reason, isn't it?

313
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,040
You really

314
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:03,440
get me, Yu.

315
00:13:03,560 --> 00:13:05,760
We need to separate the brand
from the product.

316
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,720
So what should we call it?

317
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:13,240
The recovery of the Zhous'
core Rustling Silk craft

318
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,600
was led by you, Yu.

319
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:15,960
So,

320
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:18,400
how about "Yu Silk"?

321
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:21,360
Yu Silk.

322
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,320
That sounds awful.

323
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,920
If you hate it, you name it.

324
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:29,240
Rustling Silk...

325
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:32,080
How about

326
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,920
we call it Gambiered Silk?

327
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,040
It resonates with Chunxiang's name.

328
00:13:35,680 --> 00:13:38,520
Rustling Silk to Gambiered Silk?

329
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:39,840
Nice, my lady.

330
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,520
That's a great name.

331
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:41,560
Hold on.

332
00:13:42,800 --> 00:13:43,760
What's the name?

333
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,480
- Gambiered Silk.
- Gambiered Silk.

334
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,400
Gambiered Silk?

335
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,160
Rustling Silk?

336
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,560
So that's how it came to be.

337
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,920
What are you talking about?

338
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:54,120
Uh, nothing.

339
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,000
It's not important.

340
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,320
There you are.

341
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:01,120
Come with me.

342
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,120
Hey, what are you doing?

343
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:05,400
We're busy here.

344
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:07,520
Busy with Li Yunhe? Doing what?

345
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:09,160
It's chaos outside,

346
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,720
and you're still messing around
with him?

347
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,440
Come with me.

348
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:12,440
Stop right there.

349
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,720
Whatever it is,
let's talk it out properly.

350
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,960
Keep your hands off her.

351
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,240
Stay out of this.

352
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,520
You have no say here.

353
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:21,280
You...

354
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,360
Can't deal with it?

355
00:14:22,640 --> 00:14:23,960
As a mere good-for-nothing,

356
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,600
how dare you
throw your weight around here?

357
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,760
Let's go!

358
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,400
You really think I'd fear you?

359
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,120
(Zhou's Fabrics)
This vicious shop

360
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,120
(Zhou's Fabrics)
is selling shoddy goods as top quality!

361
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,720
- I demand a refund!
- Refund!

362
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,600
- Refund!
- Refund!

363
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,400
- Give us our money back!
- Refund!

364
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,160
The Zhou family

365
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:41,440
has already lost
its imperial tribute status.

366
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,680
And they still call it
"tribute-grade quality"?

367
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,200
Frauds!

368
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,880
- Give us our money back!
- Refund!

369
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:48,440
- I demand a refund!
- Refund!

370
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,720
- Refund!
- Refund!

